    {
      "_kind": "single_choice",
      "id": "q-590",
      "text": "147. Hvilken oppgave har Pressurizing and dump valve?",
      "score": 1,
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "69edc1fb-f383-498e-8815-89b890ffddb9-opt-1",
          "label": "demand for fuel is low= fue flows through the primary manifold,"
        },
        {
          "id": "69edc1fb-f383-498e-8815-89b890ffddb9-opt-2",
          "label": "demand for fuel is high =  pressurization valve opens,  deliver fuel to the secondary manifold."
        }
      ],
      "explanations": [
        "dump valves are used to reduce pressure in a (intake) system",
        "used in duplex nozzle engine\nAt engine start, **fuel control** send pres signal to pressurization valve to close dump valve, opening fuel passage\n* demand for fuel is low= fue flows through the primary manifold,\n* demand for fuel is high =  pressurization valve opens,  deliver fuel to the secondary manifold.",
        "At engine shutdown,  dump valve  opens to drain fuel from the manifolds.",
        "![image.png](../assets/image_1710319371325_0.png)"
      ],
      "attachments": [
        [
          {
